### ── ADMIN SERVICE (/admin) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Tüm işlemler Admin rolü gerektirir.

### 1. Kullanıcıları listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 2. Rolleri listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Roles
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Şubeleri listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Branches
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 4. Yeni şube oluştur
# @name createBranch
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/createBranch
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "STU",
  "name": "AutoMarkt Stuttgart",
  "address": "Königstraße 5",
  "city": "Stuttgart",
  "country": "Deutschland",
  "region": "Baden-Württemberg"
}

### 5. Şubeyi güncelle
### branchId: 4. adımdan dönen ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/updateBranch
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branchId": "BURAYA_BRANCH_ID",
  "name": "AutoMarkt Stuttgart Zentrum",
  "address": "Königstraße 10",
  "city": "Stuttgart",
  "country": "Deutschland",
  "region": "Baden-Württemberg"
}

### 6. Şubeyi devre dışı bırak
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/disableBranch
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branchId": "BURAYA_BRANCH_ID"
}

### 7. Yeni kullanıcı oluştur
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/createUser
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator.fischer@automarkt.de",
  "firstName": "Hans",
  "lastName": "Fischer",
  "phoneNumber": "+49 711 12345678",
  "roleCode": "Operator"
}

### 8. Rol ata — yeni kullanıcıya Manager rolü ekle
### userId: 7. adımdan dönen ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/assignRole
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "BURAYA_USER_ID",
  "roleCode": "Manager"
}

### 9. Kullanıcıyı devre dışı bırak
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/disableUser
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "BURAYA_USER_ID"
}

### 10. Audit log'ları listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/AuditLogs
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 11. EventOutbox'ı listele
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/EventOutbox
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 12. Admin işlemi — Manager rolüyle (reddedilmeli)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/Users
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}